     <body>
     <div type="encomium">
   <head>To his friend the Author.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>
         <hi>I</hi> Cannot but admire this Worke of thine,</l>
      <l>(Rightworthy Author) that me thinkes each line</l>
      <l>Should gaine attention from a well tun'd Eare,</l>
      <l>And please the Eye of any shall appeare,</l>
      <l>That apprehends it: alwayes Ile attend</l>
      <l>To wish this Worke well, as a faithfull Friend.</l>
   </lg>
   <signed>IOHN MINGAY.</signed>
</div>
